Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.17,0:01:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  池袋最強？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.43,0:01:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就應該是那傢伙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.93,0:01:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平和島靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:01:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然就被公司解雇了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連宿舍也讓我馬上搬出去
